Class RDateList

  • java.lang.Object
    • biweekly.util.com.google.ical.values.RDateList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IcalObject

    public class RDateList
extends Object
    a list of dates, as from an RDATE or EXDATE ical property.

    See RFC 2445 sections 4.8.5.1 and 4.8.5.3.

    Author:
    mikesamuel+svn@gmail.com (Mike Samuel)
